SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT CLNT108_ACC_CURR, cast(SUM(CMON_CURRBALINVESTMENT) as decimal(13,2)), cast(SUM(CMON_CURRBALDEBTORS) as decimal(13,2)), cast(SUM(CMON_CURRBALRESERVE) as decimal(13,2)), cast(SUM(CMON_TOTINTERESTINCOME) as decimal(13,2)), cast(SUM(CMON_TOTCOMMISSIONINCOME) as decimal(13,2)) FROM :1/admn, :1/clnt, :1/cmon WHERE ADMN_NO = CLNT101_ADMNO and ADMN_ADMNO_RATES = :5 and CLNT108_ACC_CURR <> ':2' and CMON_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CMON_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and CMON_YEAR = :3 and CMON_MONTH = :4 and CMON_CURRENCY = CLNT108_ACC_CURR GROUP BY CLNT108_ACC_CURR ORDER BY CLNT108_ACC_CURR FOR FETCH ONLY
